OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 13 JUN
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1946FPicture Page - last broadcast in
OL,7,FAugust 1939 - is back on air, following
OL,8,FWorld War II.
OL,9,
OL,10,CG1952FThe first edition of For Deaf
OL,11,FChildren airs on BBC TV.
OL,12,
OL,13,CG1961FThe final episode of Spycatcher
OL,14,Fairs on BBC TV. Drama series, based on
OL,15,Ffact. The series follows the adventures
OL,16,Fof Colonel Pinto, the most renowned of
OL,17,FBritish interrogators during World War
OL,18,FII. Starring Bernard Archard in the
OL,19,Ftitle role.
