OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1973FThe first edition of We Are the
OL,7,FChampions airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,FAlthough the show ran until 1995, from
OL,10,F1988 the usual full series of
OL,11,Fprogrammes was replaced by one-off
OL,12,Fspecials.
OL,13,
OL,14,FThe long-running children's sports
OL,15,Fprogramme was originally presented by
OL,16,FRon Pickering. Following Ron's death in
OL,17,F1991, Gary Lineker took over as
OL,18,Fpresenter.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG1977FThe final episode of Arlott and
OL,21,FTrueman on Cricket airs on BBC Two.
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
