OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1979FThe first episode of The Omega
OL,7,FFactor airs on BBC One. The new sci-fi
OL,8,Fdrama debuted at 8.10pm. A ten-part
OL,9,Fthriller about psychic research and the
OL,10,Fparanormal. It starred James Hazeldine,
OL,11,FLouise Jameson and John Carlisle.
OL,12,
OL,13,CG1982FThe final edition of Nai Zindagi
OL,14,F- Naya Jeevan airs on BBC One. Magazine
OL,15,Fseries for viewers from India and
OL,16,FPakistan. Produced by BBC Birmingham.
OL,17,
OL,18,CG1987FThe first edition of Les
OL,19,FDennis's Laughter Show airs on BBC One.
